1.title: Christine Lakin on C'est La Vie with Selah V!

episode of.title: C'est La Vie with Selah V! (TV Series 2013– )

1.plot: Selah interviews actress Christine Lakin, a TV and film actress for more than 20 years, about what she does to stay in shape and what motivates her to workout and eat right.

2.title: Kelly Stables on C'est La Vie with Selah V!

episode of.title: C'est La Vie with Selah V! (TV Series 2013– )

2.plot: Selah interviews television's Kelly Stables on what she likes to do to workout and what motivates her to stay in shape. Find out what her favorite sinful recipe is and how to healthify it.

3.title: Ric Drasin on C'est La Vie with Selah V!

episode of.title: C'est La Vie with Selah V! (TV Series 2013– )

3.plot: Selah interviews bodybuilding and wrestling legend Ric Drasin about his history in the fitness industry and what tips he has for others looking to get in shape.

4.title: Doug Brignole on C'est La Vie with Selah V!

episode of.title: C'est La Vie with Selah V! (TV Series 2013– )

4.plot: Selah interviews Doug Brignole, former Mr. America and Mr. Universe about his training technique, diet, and what motivates him to workout.

5.title: Jen Lilley on C'est La Vie with Selah V!

episode of.title: C'est La Vie with Selah V! (TV Series 2013– )

5.plot: Selah interviews soap star and actress Jen Lilley on what her favorite workouts are and what motivates her to workout. Find out what her favorite sinful recipe is and how to healthify it.

imdb.plot outline: C'est la Vie with Selah V is a fitness talk show featuring conversations with celebrities and fitness stars about the latest and greatest in the workout world! Plus, host Selah V provides dozens of free workouts that you can combine to create your own playlist! Also check out Selah's recipe renovations and holiday segments! Learn tips on how to get and stay in the best shape of your life and choose the workout regimen that works for YOU on C'est la Vie with Selah V!
